room_title: Escape room "Medieval Madness" by PanIQ Escape Room Chicago in Chicago
review: This place has really good rooms to escape in. The staff is very friendly and helpful. I love how each escape room has multiple rooms inside it. One of the best escape rooms my friends and I have done.

room_title: Escape room "Medieval Madness" by PanIQ Escape Room Chicago in Chicago
review: Amazing room! The best we have done in the City. The use of unique puzzles is on point. Would highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Medieval Madness" by PanIQ Escape Room Chicago in Chicago
review: Fun and challenging experience. I would definitely do it again. You have to have a fun group to do it with.
